methods.release:
Release all referents previously added to this scope in its capacity as a LivenessManager, unless other
 references to this scope are retained in its capacity as a LivenessReferent.
methods.transferTo:
Transfer all retained LivenessReferents from this LivenessScope to a compatible
 LivenessManager. Transfer support compatibility is implementation defined.

:param other: (io.deephaven.engine.liveness.LivenessManager) - The other LivenessManager

text: LivenessNode implementation for providing external scope to one or more LivenessReferents.
